Date: Tue, 5 May 2026 20:04:50 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 5/5] test(auth) + docs: lock in lifecycle contract

Adds 20 Jest contract tests covering authOk, authFail,
authValidationError, authFailFromError, the AUTH_ERROR_CODES
catalogue, and the controller-level shape produced by the
authenticated change-password flow.

Adds docs/auth-contract.md describing the canonical envelope,
error catalogue, every auth endpoint, and the rules clients
should follow (branch on success + error.code, never on HTTP
status or message text).
